    "intro": "Interpretation moves from what the text says to what it means — tracing the author's argument within the larger canonical and historical context. The movements below follow 2 Kings 10's argument structure, attending to how each pericope advances the narrator's theological case about prophetic fulfillment, Jehu's character, and the nature of genuine covenant faithfulness.",
